metadata.name: THE FIRST GATHERING
metadata.description: AI has come a long way in such a short time and continues to astound me with what it comes up with. Here a welcome rabbit hole after a chance mistake made me realise I can put all my old images into an AI and specifically ask it to create a whole new vision of my previous creative incarnations. AI is not as easy as it looks, it is a fine tuning process of finding the right words in the right combination and after many failed attempts you find a gold stream but you have to make the most of it before the AI seems to get tired of the words and requires something new. I am really feeling that I am collaborating with something, from somewhere! When it clicks into place as it did with these there is a real sense of appreciation and inspiration. I am keeping my word combos secret but the REAL CUTE BLOBS title gives a big enough hint.
